<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Neutral">Neutral</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Charismatic_Christianity&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Neutral"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
